# Observability

## Token Usage

For local open-source models (e.g. Ollama), **token usage tracking is not a priority**. Focus on:

- Node/agent execution traces
- LLM call spans
- Chain/graph flow visibility

Do not add token counting or cost metrics to observability unless explicitly requested.
